## Plots

This folder contains the simulation figures generated by the MATLAB implementation of the Scalable 8×8 and 16×16 MIMO-OFDM PHY Simulator with CQI/BLER-Based Adaptive Modulation and Coding.

The plots present BER and BLER performance, estimated CQI, selected MCS index, modulation-order and coding-rate adaptation, EVM, SINR, throughput, spectral efficiency, channel capacity, and comparisons between 
the 8×8 and 16×16 MIMO configurations.

These figures are used to evaluate whether the AMC controller maintains the target BLER while selecting an appropriate modulation and coding scheme for changing channel and SNR conditions.
